<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>خ ش ي<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[١٦٢٤ - خ ش ي]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>تخشَّى يتخشَّى، تَخَشَّ، تخشّيًا، فهو متخشٍّ، والمفعول مُتخشًّى <span class="c2">(للمتعدِّي)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• تخشَّى الشَّخصُ:</span> خاف.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• تخشَّى المرضَ وغيرَه:</span> خافه، فزع منه.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>